&lt;div&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;isSelectedEnd&quot;&gt;Scorpion is looking for a Sales Account Executive to drive new business growth within the pest control industry through our AI powered marketing and technology platform. This is a true hunter role where you&#39;ll build your own pipeline, develop relationships with business owners, and own the sales process from prospecting through close.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;isSelectedEnd&quot;&gt;We&#39;re looking for someone who understands the challenges of running a pest control business and can confidently have strategic conversations about lead generation, marketing ROI, customer acquisition, and revenue growth.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;isSelectedEnd&quot;&gt;Whether you&#39;ve sold software, route management, CRM, equipment, chemicals, distribution, or other business solutions to pest control companies, your industry expertise is what matters most.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you&#39;re energized by opening new doors, winning new clients, and helping pest control businesses grow, we&#39;d love to meet you.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;What your success will look like&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;PDq2pG_selectionAnchorContainer&quot; data-section-id=&quot;19rf2ci&quot; data-start=&quot;1374&quot; data-end=&quot;1402&quot;&gt;Own the Full Sales Cycle:&amp;nbsp; Generate and close new business by owning the sales process from prospecting through discovery, demonstration, proposal, negotiation, and close.&lt;/li&gt;
