&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;5+ Years of Experience or Relevant Experience.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Developing production-grade Python services at scale.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Operating real-time or high-throughput infrastructure supporting AI/ML workloads.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Designing and operating distributed, event-driven systems in production environments.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
